document_data.History:
Hunters claimed to have killed a "globular", possibly a [[deepspawn]], some years before in {{yearlink|1368}}.

In {{yearlink|1365}}, an [[Aglarond]]an force returned to Aglarond through the Gap after pushing an enemy Thayan force out of [[Shyvar Pass]] in order to flank another Thayan force as it attacked Emmech.{{cite book/The Grand History of the Realms|147}}

In {{yearlink|1479}}, [[Vunmal Murn]] of [[Phsant]] fomented a rivalry between her home city and [[Aglarond]] over the Tannath Gap.{{cite book/Forgotten Realms Campaign Guide|182}}
